'From Squeak 2.5 of August 6, 1999 [latest update: #1538] on 11 October 1999 at 4:51:24 pm'!"Change Set:		BezierFixDate:			11 October 1999Author:			Andreas RaabFixes a problem with the number of segments when drawing bezier shapes."!!BalloonEngine methodsFor: 'drawing' stamp: 'ar 10/11/1999 16:49'!drawBezierShape: points fill: fillStyle borderWidth: borderWidth borderColor: borderFill transform: aTransform	| fills |	self edgeTransform: aTransform.	self resetIfNeeded.	fills _ self registerFill: fillStyle and: borderFill.	self primAddBezierShape: points		segments: (points size) // 3		fill: (fills at: 1)		lineWidth: borderWidth		lineFill: (fills at: 2).	self postFlushIfNeeded.! !